    >>> triples_sum_to_zero([2, 4, -5, 3, 9, 7])

    >>> triples_sum_to_zero([1])
    False
    """

    for i in range(len(l)):
        if i == 0:
            sum_of_three += l[i]
        elif i == len(l) - 1:
            sum_of_three += l[i]
        else:

    return sum_of_three == 0
